Playercard/Black Ops II Calling Cards

< Playercard
Edit
  • VisualEditor
  • History
  • Talk (0)
Share


In Call of Duty: Black Ops II, there are calling cards which can be unlocked via completing challenges, purchasing DLC or through simply levelling up.

Contents

[show]

    List of Calling Cards in Black Ops IIEdit

     [Expand] 

    General Calling CardsEdit

    1. Hexed - Default Calling Card.
    2. Grizzled Veteran - Earn 1,500,000 score from Public Games
    3. Career Wins - Win 500 matches
    4. Top 3 Player - Complete 250 matches among the Top 3 players
    5. Hardcore Veteran - Earn 100,000 from Hardcore Public Games
    6. Hardcore Vanquisher - Win 250 Hardcore matches
    7. Hardcore Superior - Complete 250 Hardcore matches among the Top 3 players
    8. Multi-Team Veteran - Earn 100,000 score from Multi-Team Public Games
    9. Multi-Team Vanquisher - Win ? Multi-Team matches
    10. Multi-Team Superior - Complete ? Multi-Team matches among the Top 3 players
    11. Operations Master - Completed all Career Operations challenges
    12. Career Kills - Get 10,000 Kills
    13. Career Headshots - Get 1,000 Headshots
    14. Return to Sender - Get 25 kills with thrown back grenades
    15. Movie Star - Get featured in the Final Kill Cam 25 times
    16. Situational Awareness - Kill 25 enemies by triggering a car to explode
    17. Precision Master - Earn all Precision unlocks
    18. Master Chef - Kill 50 enemies with a cooked grenade
    19. Backfire - Get 25 Backfire medals (kill the enemy with their own weapon)
    20. Heartbreaker - Get 25 Buzz Kill medals (killed an enemy to stop their kill streak)
    23. From the Grave - Get 25 Afterlife medals (killed an enemy after you have died)
    24. Sneak Attack - Get 25 Backstabber medals (knife an enemy in the back)
    25. Unforgiving - Get 25 Revenge medals (killed the enemy who killed you)
    26. Sticky Bomber - Get 25 Stick medals (killed the enemy by sticking them with an explosive)
    27. Bloodthirsty Killer - Earn 30 Bloodthirsty medals (5 kills without dying)
    28. Merciless Killer - Earn 15 Merciless medals (10 kills without dying)
    29. Ruthless Killer - Earn 5 Ruthless medals (15 kills without dying)
    30. Relentless Killer - Earn 3 Relentless medals (20 kills without dying)
    31. Nuclear Killer - Earn a Nuclear medal (30 kills without dying)
    32. Double Killer - Earn 20 Double Kill medals (2 rapid kills)
    33. Triple Killer - Earn 20 Triple Kill medals (3 rapid kills)
    34. Mega Killer - Get 1 Mega Kill (7 rapid kills)
    35. Ultra Killer - Get 1 Ultra Kill (8 rapid kills)
    36. Chain Killer - Get a Kill Chain (killed more than 8 players rapidly)
    37. Feed Greed - Earn 10 Quad Feed medals (4 uninterrupted kills in the kill feed)
    38. Master Killer - Earn all Killer unlocks
    39. X Ray Vision - Kill 50 enemies by shooting them though objects
    40. Spotter - Kill 50 enemies that are prone
    41. Laid to Rest - Kill 50 enemies while prone
    42. Stalking Prey - Kill 50 enemies while crouched
    43. Eyes in the Sky - Kill 100 enemies while your Orbital VSAT is active
    44. Down and Out - Kill 100 players while your EMP is active
    45. UAV Support - Get 5,000 Assist Score from the UAV
    46. EMP Support - Get 2,500 Assist Score from the EMP
    47. Orbital VSAT Support - Get 2,500 Assist Score from the Orbital VSAT
    48. Hunter Killer Kills - Get 50 kills with the Hunter Killer
    49. Hellstorm Missile Kills - Get 50 kills with the Hellstorm Missile
    50. Lightning Strike Kills - Get 50 kills with the Lightning Strike
    51. Dragonfire Kills - Get 50 kills with the Dragonfire
    52. Stealth Chopper Kills - Get 50 kills with the Stealth Chopper
    53. Escort Drone Kills - Get 50 kills with the Escort Drone
    54. Warthog Kills - Get 50 kills with the Warthog
    55. Lodestar Kills - Get 50 kills with the Lodestar
    56. VTOL Warship Kills - Get 50 kills with the VTOL Warship
    57. Swarm Kills - Get 50 kills with the Swarm
    58. RC-XD Kills - Get 50 kills with the RC-XD
    59. Sentry Gun Kills - Get 50 kills with the Sentry Gun
    60. Death Machine Kills - Get 50 kills with the Death Machine
    61. War Machine Kills - Get 50 kills with the War Machine
    62. A.G.R. Kills - Get 50 kills with the A.G.R.
    63. K9 Unit Kills - Get 50 kills with the K9 unit
    64. Primary Mastery - Achieve mastery for every Primary Weapon
    65. Secondary Mastery - Achieve mastery for every Secondary Weapon
    66. Weapons Mastery - Complete weapon mastery for primary and secondary weapons to earn your Diamond Combat Knife Camo.
    67. Assault Rifle Kills - Get 1,000 Kills with Assault Rifle
    68. Submachine Gun Kills - Get 1,000 Kills with Submachine Gun
    69. Light Machine Gun Kills - Get 1,000 Kills with Light Machine Gun
    70. Shotgun Kills - Get 1,000 kills with Shotgun
    71. Sniper Rifle Kills - Get 1,000 kills with Sniper Rifle
    72. Pistol Kills - Get 1,000 kills with Pistol
    73. Scorestreak Kills - Get 1,000 kills with Scorestreak
    74. Scorestreak Assist - Get 10,000 Assist Score from Scorestreaks
    75. Actionable Intel - Kill 100 enemies while your UAV is in the air
    76. Baked to Perfection - Kill 100 players that are being damaged by your Guardian (does not include kills by the Guardian)
    77. Counter Intelligence - Kill 100 enemies while your Counter-UAV is in the air
    78. Guardian Support - Get 500 Assist Score from the Guardian
    79. Counter UAV Support - Get 5,000 Assist Score from the Counter-UAV
    80. Reflex Sight Master - Earn all Reflex Sight Reticles
    81. ACOG Sight Master - Earn all ACOG Sight Reticles
    82. EOTech Sight Master - Earn all EOTech Sight Reticles
    83. Hybrid Optic Master - Earn all Hybrid Optic Reticles
    84. Anti-Air Specialist - Shoot down an enemy Aircraft 75 times
    85. Junkyard - Destroy enemy Sentry Gun or Guardian 50 times
    86. Boot Camp Graduate - Earn All Boot Camp unlocks
    87. Master of Humiliation - Earn all Humiliation Unlocks

    Prestige Calling Cards (Accessible at level 1 Prestige 1)Edit

    1. Target Finder Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights with the Target Finder.
    2. Milimeter Scanner Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights with the Millimeter Scanner.
    3. Iron Sights Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights with the Iron Sight.
    4. Dual Band Scope Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights with the Dual band Scope.
    5. Extended Clip Kills- Get 500 kills using the Extend Clip attachment.
    6. Rapid Fire Kills- Get 500 kills using the Rapid Fire attachment.
    7. Suppressor Kills- Get 500 kills using the Suppressor attachment.
    8. Long Barrel Kills- Get 500 kills using the Long Barrel attachment.
    9. Laser Sight Kills- Get 500 kills using the Laser Sight attachment.
    10. Dual Wield Kills- Get 500 kills using the Dual Wield attachment.
    11. Variable Zoom Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights with the Variable Zoom.
    12. Fore Grip Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights using the Fore Grip attachment.
    13. Quickdraw Handle Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights using the Quickdraw Handle attachment.
    14. Adjustable Stock Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights using the Adjustable Stock attachment.
    15. Ballistics CPU Kills- Get 500 kills while aiming down sights with the Ballistics CPU.
    16. Grenade Launcher Kills- Get 300 kills using the Grenade Launcher attachment.
    23. Select Fire Kills- Kill 300 enemies using select fire.
    24. Full Metal Jacket- Get 300 kills by shooting through walls with FMJ.
    26. Tactical Knife- Get 100 kills using the Tactical Knife attachment.
    25. Fast Mag- Use Fast Mag and kill an enemy within 5 seconds of reloading 300 times.
    60. Tri-Bolt Kills- Get 500 Kills with the Tri-Bolt Attachment.
    17. Grenade Kills- Get 300 Grenade Kills.
    18. Combat Axe Kills- Get 300 Combat Axe Kills.
    19. Semtex Kills- Get 300 Semtex Kills.
    20. C4 Kills- Get 300 C4 Kills.
    21. Bouncing Betty Kills- Get 300 Bouncing Betty Kills.
    22. Claymore Kills- Get 300 Kills with Claymores.
    27. Shock Charge- Kill 300 players that are stunned by your Shock Charge.
    28. EMP Grenade- Destroy 300 pieces of equipment with the EMP grenade.
    29. Concussion- Kill 300 players that are stunned by your Concussion.
    30. Flashbang- Kill 300 players that are stunned by your Flashbang.
    31. Smoke Grenade - Capture 100 objectives under the cover of your smoke grenade
    32. Tactical Insertion- Get 100 kills within 5 seconds of Tactical Insertion.
    33. Sensor Grenade- Kill 300 Players detected by your Sensor Grenade.
    34. Trophy System- Destroy 100 enemy projectiles with the Trophy System.
    35. Black Hat- Hack 300 pieces of equipment or Scorestreaks with your Black Hat.
    36. Flak Jacket- Survive 100 explosives while using Flak Jacket.
    37. Ghost- Kill 100 enemies while they have a UAV (and you have Ghost equipped).
    38. Blind Eye- Destroy 200 Enemy AI controlled aircraft while using Blind Eye.
    39. Hardline- Earn 200 Scorestreaks while using Hardline.
    40. Lightweight- Kill 500 enemies while using Lightweight.
    41. Cold Blooded- Kill 500 enemies while using Cold Blooded.
    42. Hard Wired- Kill 100 enemies while there is an Enemy Counter UAV or EMP Systems Active.
    43. Scavenger- Get 250 kills after resupplying ammo or explosives using Scavenger.
    44. Fast Hands- Get 100 kills within 5 seconds of swapping weapons using Fast Hands.
    45. Toughness- Kill 100 enemies after taking damage while using Toughness.
    46. Engineer- Hack or destroy 250 pieces of enemy equipment while using Engineer.
    47. Dead Silence- Kill 500 enemies while using Dead Silence.
    48. Extreme Conditioning- Kill 200 enemies after sprinting while using Extreme Conditioning.
    49. Tactical Mask- Kill 100 enemies stunned by your Flashbang, Shock Charge or Concussion while using Tactical Mask.
    50. Dexterity- Kill 100 enemies while aiming down sights after sprinting while using Dexterity.
    51. Awareness- Get 500 kills with Awareness equipped.
    52. Primary Gunfighter- Get 500 kills with a weapon that has 3 attachments.
    53. Secondary Gunfighter- Get 500 kills with 2 attachments on your Secondary Weapon.
    54. Overkill- Get a kill with your Primary and Secondary Weapon in the same life 500 times while using Overkill.
    55. Danger Close- Get 100 kills using Lethals when playing with a Class that has 2 Lethals equipped.
    56. Tactician- Get 500 kills when playing with 2 different Tacticals equipped.
    57. Perk 1 Greed- Get 500 kills when playing with a class that has 2 perks from Perk 1.
    58. Perk 2 Greed- Get 500 kills when playing with a class that has 2 perks from Perk 2.
    59. Perk 3 Greed- Get 500 kills when playing with a class that has 2 perks from Perk 3.

    TriviaEdit

    • In game the "Defender" calling cards (46-49 under Game Modes) do not state the game mode they must be earned in.
    • Despite their descriptions, the "Primary Mastery", "Secondary Mastery" and "Weapons Mastery" calling cards do not require Mastery on each weapon, as only Expert on each weapon (except Peacekeeper) will suffice.
      • Moreover, the "Weapons Mastery" calling card's description states Diamond Camouflage for Combat Knife is unlocked by completing Mastery for every weapon, while it is actually earned by completing all camouflage challenges for all Special weapons.
    • Under Prestige Calling Cards, the character featured in Perk 1 Greed is green, and the character in Perk 2 Greed is blue. Upon looking at the perks in both tiers, their colors should be reversed assuming they are colored that way to represent the perks.
